Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒和一君這樣悠閒過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 一君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道城裏人要來這裡的消息麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點 害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈美 我們做什麼錯事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用擔心了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛想到的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 一君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍受這點還是很輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}用我這隻手奪取一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}即使心靈受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}覺醒的本能不斷驅使著身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}語言能改變本義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}昨天的真實 今天就變成了謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}誰都只能在彷徨中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:02:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,300)}夢想和愛等等不過是作為托詞的美妙幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}進入現實 則沒有結果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}伸出手把握明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Reckless fire 如此大膽地點燃了靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}無處可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}與將謊言和矛盾一飲而盡的力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}現在不奢望 深藏在彼此心中的 Sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}不交給任何人 直到我掌握到了某樣東西...
